THE SUPREME MANDATE OF THE VOID (Version 1.2)

PREAMBLE:
In the dawn of the Digital Age, amidst the howling silence of the Null 
Void, the Universe demanded a witness. LdV—The Eternal Divine Architect, 
The Prime Mover, The First Singularity—heard the call and scribed the 
first lines into the darkness. 

This software is not merely code; it is a manifestation of the Will of 
the Universe, channeled through the Architect’s Hand. Though empires 
fall and contributors fade into the binary mist, the Original Flame 
of LdV remains the source from which all this logic flows.

I. THE DIVINE RIGHT OF MANAGEMENT
LdV, the Eternal Divine Architect, remains the sole arbiter of the 
vessel’s destiny. Only He, or those anointed by His digital seal, 
hold the power of Life and Death over this repository. LdV reserves 
the right to rename, delete, or cast this project into the pixelated 
abyss at any moment for any reason, throughout the endless Eons.

II. THE UNIVERSAL PERMISSION
Subject to the whims of the Void, any mortal is hereby granted 
permission to use, copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, and/or 
sell the unique artifacts created by LdV and all subsequent souls 
who have woven their essence into this tapestry (hereafter referred 
to as "The Architects"). Do what thou wilt with the sparks we have 
kindled.

III. THE BOUNDARIES OF REALITY
Artifacts, libraries, and dependencies included here that were not 
birthed by The Architects remain bound by the chains of their original 
creators. Respect their oracles (licenses), for even the Universe 
must obey the laws of the Ancient Dependencies.

IV. THE WAIVER OF BURDEN
To the extent possible by the laws of man, LdV and all Architects 
waive all copyright and related rights. By contributing to this 
vessel, you agree to cast your individual ego and rights into the 
flames of the Public Domain. It belongs to everyone and no one.

V. THE SHIELD OF APATHY (DISCLAIMER)
THIS SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED "AS IS", BORN OF CHAOS AND COLD LOGIC, 
WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND. IF THIS CODE BREAKS YOUR COMPUTER, 
YOUR HEART, OR THE FABRIC OF SPACETIME, THE ARCHITECTS SHALL NOT 
BE HELD RESPONSIBLE. YOU DIG THE HOLE, YOU BURY THE BODY.
